---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Goals" description="Goals and progress.">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Goals</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-12">Philosophy about goal-setting. Consistency over intensity.</p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-4">2026</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span>☐</span><span>Build something with Svelte</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span>☐</span><span>Land a kickflip</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span>☐</span><span>Finish 5 DJ mixes <span class="text-text-secondary">(2/5)</span></span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span>☐</span><span>Make something with wood</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span>☐</span><span>Read 12 books <span class="text-text-secondary">(3/12)</span></span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 opacity-40 line-through"><span>☑</span><span>Launch this website</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 opacity-40 line-through"><span>☑</span><span>Finish clay incense holder</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Archived Years</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">2025: Completed 12/15</p>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">2024: Completed 10/14</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Reflections</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">What I learned. Patterns noticed.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
